<exercises>
    <exercise>
        <statement>
            <p>Refer back to question <xref ref="mat-trans-qn-2"/>
                <ol>
                    <li>Is <m>T</m> one-to-one?</li>
                    <li>Is <m>T</m> onto?</li>
                </ol>
            </p>
        </statement>
        <answer>
            <p>
                <ol>
                    <li>The transformation <m>T</m> is one-to-one if and only if <m>A</m> has a pivot in each column, which it does (it is already in row echelon form).</li>
                    <li>The transformation <m>T</m> is onto if and only if <m>A</m> has a pivot in each row, which it does not.</li>
                </ol>
            </p>
        </answer>
    </exercise>
</exercises>
